quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"ﾆ‘en yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,2,"Gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 ngolli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe, ﾉ兎 ngooﾅ極擁ni ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immorﾉ熔 e Joomi maﾉ橡兎 - O yawtanii ﾉ兎 bonﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, O moﾆｴﾆｴinii fiyaaku maﾉ橡兎 oon."
  47,3,"Ko waﾉ擁 ﾉ蓉um, ko tawde yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n njokkii mehre nden, gooﾅ極擁inﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kan njokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi maﾉ橡兎 on. Ko wano nii Allah fiyiranta yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n yeru maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  47,4,"Si on kawri e yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en (ka hare), ko soppugol daaﾉ容 ﾉ容en. Haa si on ﾉ蓉ﾉ遼擁nii bargol ﾉ兎, kaﾉ橡登n koyﾉ容 ﾉ容n. Ko si on moﾆｴﾆｴora e maﾉ橡兎 ngaccitugol ﾉ兎 ﾉ殿awo ﾉ蓉um, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare ndeen wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non ﾃｱaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e maﾉ橡兎, ko woni tan, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. Waraaﾉ兎 fii Allah ﾉ兎en, pellet, O yeebataa golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,5,"Arma O feewna ﾉ兎, O moﾆｴﾆｴina fiyaaku maﾉ橡兎,"
  47,6,"O naatnya ﾉ兎 Aljanna, mo O anndini ﾉ兎 fii mum."
  47,7,"Eey mon yo gooﾅ極擁inﾉ兎, si on ngonii wallooﾉ兎 fii Allah, O wallat on, O tabintina teppe mon ﾉ容n."
  47,8,"Yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎e kan, halkaare woodanii ﾉ兎, O majjinii kadi golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,9,"ﾆ隔um le ko tawde ﾉ兎 aﾃｱii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,10,"E ﾉ兎e njiilaaki e leydi ndin, ﾉ兎 teskoo ko honno battane adinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii maﾉ橡兎. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  47,11,"Ko waﾉ擁 ﾉ蓉m, ko tawde ko Allah woni giﾉ熔 gooﾅ極擁inﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en; hara non yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, giﾉ熔 (woo) alanaa ﾉ兎."
  47,12,"Pellet, Allah naatnoyat gooﾅ極擁inﾉ兎 ngolli moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ擁 ﾉ兎n, Aljannaaji ﾉ擁 canﾉ擁 ilata ley (kuﾉ兎eje) majje. Yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en kan, heﾉ兎 ndakmitoo, ﾉ兎 ﾃｱaamira wano neemoraaﾉ擁 ﾉ擁in ﾃｱaamirta; hara noon ko Yiite nge woni jaaﾆｴorde maﾉ橡兎."
  47,13,"ﾆ隔uﾉ擁i e ca'e, ﾉ砥rnooﾉ兎 tiiﾉ蓉de semmbe, e dii ndeen saare maa raﾉ擁inde ma, ﾉ兎 Moen kalki, ballo alanaa ﾉ兎."
  47,14,"Kere ko on gonﾉ熔 e ﾉ殿nngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mum, wa'i wa ﾉ兎en cuﾉ擁nanaaﾉ兎 kuuﾉ容 mun bonﾉ容 ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 jokki beleeﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎?"
  47,15,"Ko woni sifa Aljanna podaaﾉ熔 on gooﾅ極蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en: ina toon canﾉ擁 ndiyam ﾉ擁 dakamme mum waylaaki, e caatli ﾉ妬ra ﾉ擁 waylataa dakamme mum, e caatli konnjam mbelayﾉ預m yarooﾉ兎, e caatlii njuuri laﾉ橡妬naandi. Hino woodani ﾉ兎 kadi ton: kala dimﾉ兎, e haforaneede immorde e Joomi maﾉ橡兎. [ﾆ‘en wa'oyay] wa luttinoyteeeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka Yiite, ﾉ兎 njarnee ndiyam fatayﾉ預m, ﾉ預m taﾆｴa tekteki maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n?"
  47,16,"Hino e maﾉ橡兎 heﾉ擁totooﾉ兎 ma. Kono ko haa si ﾉ兎 yaltii ka maaﾉ預, ﾉ兎 wi'ana okkaaﾉ兎 ganndal ﾉ兎en: ""Ko holﾉ蓉m dee, o wi'unoo naanen?"" Ko ﾉ兎n woni ﾉ兎 Allah noti e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mum ﾉ容en, ﾉ兎 njokki mbeleeﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,17,"Feewuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en kan, O ﾉ兎ydu ﾉ兎 peewal O okkiﾉ兎 gooﾅ杵iﾉ預l maﾉ橡兎."
  47,18,"Hara ﾉ兎e no kabbbii si wonaa Darngal ngal nde ardata ﾉ兎 e juhal? Gooﾅ極擁i le Ma'andeeji maggal arii. Ko holno ﾉ兎 mbaajitoroyta, si ngal ardanii ﾉ兎 (juhal)?"
  47,19,"Awa anndu pellet, deweteeﾉ熔 alaa si wonaa Allah, imsinanoﾉ預a bakkati maa ﾉ擁n, e gooﾅ極擁inﾉ兎 worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en e gooﾅ極擁inﾉ兎 rewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n. Allah no anndi ﾃｱallirde mon e hiirirde mon."
  47,20,"Gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n hino mbi'a: ""Hara non cortewol (simoore) jippotono!"" Si tawii le cortewol ﾃｱeﾃｱaangol jippinaama, fii hare jaﾅ逆aama e maggol, a tinay ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 ﾃｱawu woni e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mum hino ndaare, ndaarﾉ容 mo maayde faﾉ遼擁ni. Ko haanannoo ﾉ兎,"
  47,21,"ko ﾉ熔ftagol e konngol moﾆｴﾆｴol. Si fiyaaku o fellitii, ﾉ兎 ngooﾅ極擁nno Allah, ko ﾉ蓉um ﾉ砥ratnoo moﾆｴﾆｴannde ﾉ兎."
  47,22,"E on tamﾆｴinaaki, si wonii on ﾉ蓉urnima nde mbonnoton e leydi ndin, taﾆｴon enﾉ預maaji mon?"
  47,23,"Ko ﾉ兎en ngoni ﾉ兎 Allah huﾉ擁 ﾉ兎en, O fa'aﾉ擁ni ﾉ兎, O wumini giiﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,24,"E ﾉ兎e tasktaako Alqur'aana, ka ko cokirﾉ容 woni woni e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mum en?"
  47,25,"Pellet, ﾉ兎en ruttorﾉ兎 ﾉ殿bbe mum ﾉ殿awo nde peewal ngal ﾉ殿nngannoo ﾉ兎, ko seytaane cuﾉ擁nani ﾉ兎, o hodi ﾉ兎."
  47,26,"Ko tawde ﾉ兎 mbi'anii ﾉ兎en aﾃｱuﾉ兎 ko Allah jippini kon: ""Min ﾉ熔ftoto on e yoga e piiji"". Allah non no anndi gunndooji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁in."
  47,27,"Ko honno (ﾉ兎e mba'oyta) tuma nde Malaa'ika'en timmini fii maﾉ橡兎, hara hiﾉ兎 bantoo j'eece maﾉ橡兎 e dote maﾉ橡兎?"
  47,28,"Ko tawde ko ﾉ兎 njokkii ko tikkinta Allah, ﾉ兎 aﾃｱii welayﾉ擁 Mo ﾉ擁in, O bonni fii golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,29,"Kaa ﾉ兎en ﾉ兎 ﾃｱawu woni e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mum sikuu won'de Allah yaltintaa ngaynguuji maﾉ橡兎?"
  47,30,"Sinno Min kaajuno, Min kolleteno ﾉ兎. Ganndiraa ﾉ兎 Ma'andeeji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁in; ko pellet, a nganndiratno ﾉ兎 ka konngol belngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon ﾉ容en."
  47,31,"Ma Min njarribo on, haa Min ngannda tiiﾉ溶iiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e mon, e muﾃｱﾃｱiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en. Min njarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon."
  47,32,"Pellet, yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en ﾉ兎 paddi laawol Allah ngol, ﾉ兎 lunndii Nulaaﾉ熔 on ﾉ殿awo nde peewal ngal ﾉ殿nngannde ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎en lorrataa Allah hay hu'unde. Ma O bonnu fii golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容en."
  47,33,"Eey mon yo gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎! ﾉ熔ftee Allah, ﾉ熔ftoﾉ熔n Nulaaﾉ熔 on, wata on mbonnu golle mon ﾉ容en."
  47,34,"Pellet, ﾉ兎en yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti ﾉ兎 maayi ko ﾉ兎 he'eferﾉ兎, Allah haforanoytaa ﾉ兎."
  47,35,"Wota on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni fooluﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njoﾉ電i golle mon ﾉ容en."
  47,36,"Ganndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbeleeﾉ容 tan; hara le si on ngooﾅ極擁ii, on kulii [Allah], O yeﾉ預y on njoﾉ電i mon ndiin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon ﾉ容en."
  47,37,"Si O aru laﾉ渡daade on fii majje, haa O duﾃｱii on (e mum), nguddon, O feﾃｱﾃｱina noon konnaagu mon ngun."
  47,38,"Hey mon onon ﾉ熔o, hoﾉ熔n noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wuddatﾉ兎. Kala non gudduﾉ熔, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon ngoni wa'asuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en. Si on nduﾅ逆ii, O waﾉ葉itira on woﾉ橡兎 goo, hara non ﾉ兎en mba'ataa wano mon."
